# Apple Liquid Glass Design System (2025)

You are implementing Apple's latest "Liquid Glass" design system - a translucent, dynamic material that unifies Apple's cross-platform design language. Follow these rules exactly. Prioritize clarity, content-first approach, and elegant vitality.

